text: Birch House may refer to: * Birch House (Falls Church, Virginia) * Birch Island House, in Somerset County, Maine * Annie Birch House, Hoytsville, Utah, listed on the National Register of Historic Places * W. Taylor Birch House, Washington, D.C., designed by Thomas Franklin Schneider * Caccia Birch House, in New Zealand ==See also== *Burch House (disambiguation)
